    "name": {
      "zh": "Aimpoint CS 反射式瞄准镜",
      "en": "Aimpoint CS reflex sight"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "CS",
      "en": "CS"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Aimpoint CS是一款现已停产的专用红点瞄准镜，专为军用步枪设计（主要为瑞典AK-5）。其特点包括：30毫米硬质阳极氧化镜筒、高效电路延长电池续航，以及独特的带通滤镜涂层以实现夜视兼容性。",
      "en": "The Aimpoint CS is a specialized, now discontinued, red dot optic designed for use with military rifles, primarily the Swedish AK-5. It features a hard-anodized 30mm tube, a high-efficiency circuit for extended battery life, and a unique band-pass coating for night vision compatibility."
    },
